verbose_text: Overexpressed CDC25A may interact with tumor associated factors including mitogen activated protein kinase kinase kinase 5, NF-kappaB, STAT3, NIMA related kinase 11, pyruvate kinase M1/2 and forkhead box O1 to promote tumor progression.
